    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty in person! It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, it\u2019s basically spotless inside and out. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand new price tag, this is the one! Drop me a message and come take it for a spin! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
