      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S. This wide-body 996.2 is powered by a 3.6L flat-six mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. Mechanical provenance is impeccable, featuring a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a comprehensive cooling system refresh. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by a corner-balanced suspension setup with zero bushing deflection. The Arctic Silver Metallic finish retains factory-spec paint depth, and the Graphite Grey leather interior shows no bolster wear or UV degradation. A clean DME report confirms no Type 2 over-revs, ensuring the valvetrain remains in peak operating condition. This is a turnkey, collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
