    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s specimen, preserved in a climate-controlled garage and maintained with an open checkbook. The exterior finish retains its original factory luster, entirely free from rock chips, swirls, or surface imperfections, while the alloy wheels show absolutely no signs of curb rash or pitting. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and taut without a single crease, and the interior still carries a faint 'new car' scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control and ambient lighting, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive, document-verified service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified master technicians. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body, reflecting a life spent away from rain and harsh elements. This is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule quality vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 43900.0,
